XM$1 PAD|VDD PAD|VDD PAD|VDD PAD|VDD PMOS L=2u W=500u AS=3523.04p AD=3523.04p
+ PS=689.36u PD=689.36u
* device instance $11 r90 *1 130,-65.5 NMOSE
XM$11 PAD|VDD VSS VSS VSS NMOSE L=2u W=500u AS=3523.04p AD=3523.04p PS=689.36u
+ PD=689.36u
.ENDS OSS_ESD_5V_VDD

